I had beige carpet in my apartment and spilled red wine and I got it out. I bought Isopropyl alcohol 90% (90% rubbing alcohol) and soak the stain with the alcohol and blot it. since I have no stains to show you, here's a link to someone who does it with only 70% rubbing alcohol. FYI I normally buy mine at the dollar store.
https://youtu.be/F52QvHmwyco
